::Hakibuscon::

	Hakibuscon wasn't angry this time when his missile hadn't hit them. 
Instead laughed for a bit.

	"Oh I'm soooo sorry!  Awww, did I bother you?  I sure hope so!!!  Wait,
stop for a sec.  Let me guess, Mr. I'm So Slick But In Bad Pain Dinosaur is
going to try to destroy me and make sure that I don't touch Beauty Wolf
over there.  Am I right?" Hakibuscon said, hollering loudly in laughter.
